@startuml
title UC07 - Gerar Código do Cupom

actor Aluno as A
boundary "Perfil do Aluno\nNext.js" as Front
control "ResgateVantagemController\nMicronaut" as Ctrl
control "CupomService" as CupomService
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

A -> Front: Confirma resgate da vantagem
Front -> Ctrl: POST /resgates
Ctrl -> Ctrl: Valida aluno, vantagem, saldo e estoque
Ctrl -> CupomService: gerarCodigoCupom(resgate)
CupomService -> CupomService: Gera código único
CupomService --> Ctrl: Código do cupom
Ctrl -> DB: Salva resgate com código do cupom
DB --> Ctrl: Resgate salvo
Ctrl --> Front: 201 Created\n{resgate, codigoCupom}
Front --> A: Exibe confirmação do resgate

@enduml
